It's nice to wake up early once in a while; I met an interesting person.

4
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:19,870
Nonohara!

5
00:00:19,870 --> 00:00:20,770
Come over here, Nonohara.

6
00:00:21,010 --> 00:00:25,040
Your opponent is this combat butler, Nonohara Kaede.

7
00:00:26,030 --> 00:00:28,510
A butler is one who serves.

8
00:00:29,250 --> 00:00:32,010
A butler is one who dedicates himself.

9
00:00:32,530 --> 00:00:38,000
A butler is a formal guardian who supports the days of their master.

10
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,260
Yes.

11
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:47,900
This is a super combat battle story of a boy who fights, risking his life for a girl.

12
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:51,910
Yes! Today will be a kendo showdown!

13
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:36,960
Your opponent will be my butler, Nonohara Kaede.

14
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,990
Butler?

15
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:43,720
So hello, I'm Nonohara Kaede.

16
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:47,380
I'm a butler of the Azumamiya family.

17
00:02:48,810 --> 00:02:50,180
He's a butler, too?

18
00:02:53,070 --> 00:02:54,910
It's him, Nonohara.

19
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:57,110
Knock him out right now!

20
00:02:57,110 --> 00:02:58,520
As you order.

21
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,720
But before that...

22
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:11,130
Down, diagonal left down, left, kick.

23
00:03:11,130 --> 00:03:12,740
It's not a Hurri**** Kick!

24
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,120
N-Nonohara, what are you...

25
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:21,330
Sir, did I not teach you?

26
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:24,520
If you are a man, put up a fight even if you know you would lose.

27
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:32,030
Yet, you rely on others without fighting, and you don't do anything.

28
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:33,960
I don't recall...

29
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:38,160
...raising you to be such a weakling!

30
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:42,030
Y-You wouldn't go that far, would you, Himuro?

31
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:45,670
Nonohara-kun is strict as always.

32
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,610
But is it all right?

33
00:03:47,990 --> 00:03:49,850
He's a butler, yet he's...

34
00:03:49,850 --> 00:03:51,940
What are you talking about?

35
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:56,280
We butlers aren't our masters' tools.

36
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:59,740
Just doing what they tell us to do isn't everything.

37
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:04,660
"Butler" used to be a highly honorable position that only the first born of a noble family could become.

38
00:04:05,410 --> 00:04:08,440
In other words, there's that much responsibility involved in the position.

39
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:11,380
The responsibility to guide one's master along the right course.

40
00:04:15,170 --> 00:04:19,840
Isn't that why you wanted to teach her the pleasure of sports?

41
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:23,680
