43
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:31,980
I-I'm sorry, Nonohara!

44
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,810
I got it! I got it!

45
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:36,450
No. I won't forgive you today.

46
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:40,480
