51
00:04:57,850 --> 00:05:02,630
This is our educational style, so would you please not interfere?

52
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:05,620
I'm sorry, but I really can't do that.

53
00:05:05,620 --> 00:05:10,860
I'm the Student Council President,
so I can't stop myself from helping a student in need.

54
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:12,160
Katsura-san...

55
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:17,200
Even if Azumamiya-kun is a weak and pathetic crybaby, I have to help him.

56
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,920
Huh?

57
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,020
Wonderful, President.

58
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:24,960
Way to strike directly at the opponent's vital point.

59
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,510
I didn't hit his vital point!

60
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,100
Okay, I get it, Nonohara.

61
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,000
I can't be weak anymore!

62
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,930
Sir!

63
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:39,620
A man must fight and open his own path!

64
00:05:39,620 --> 00:05:42,650
Sir! So you understand!

65
00:05:42,650 --> 00:05:43,450
Therefore!

66
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,240
Fight me, Sanzenin!

67
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,180
EHH?!

68
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:51,690
Um, Azumamiya-kun. May I ask the reason?

69
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:52,860
I promise I won't get angry.

70
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,670
I understand what my mistake was.

71
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,380
It's weird for the master and the butler to fight.

72
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:01,700
Or rather, there's no chance.

73
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:06,010
