75
00:06:09,210 --> 00:06:10,500
No, I don't think so.

76
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:14,890
Looks like it's hard for butlers to lead their master down the correct course.

77
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:17,490
Master! That's wonderful!

78
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:21,710
So you finally understand that.

79
00:06:21,710 --> 00:06:23,360
So you're fine with that...

80
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:26,640
So they say, Nagi. What are you going to do?

81
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,710
Don't ask me.

82
00:06:29,610 --> 00:06:31,220
Oh, fine.

83
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:36,470
Then I'll fight against Azumamiya-kun.

84
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,670
Hey, Hinagiku?

85
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:43,860
If you start swinging swords all of a sudden,
your body's going to break,

86
