169
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:55,800
Excuse us now.

170
00:12:56,890 --> 00:13:02,160
I'd be happy if you had an ultimate move ready by the next time we meet.

171
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:06,830
Then I can put up a more serious fight.

172
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,060
So?

173
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:15,140
